    "title": "executor: improve parallel hash aggregation",
    "body": "<!--\r\n\r\nThank you for contributing to TiDB!\r\n\r\nPR Title Format:\r\n1. pkg [, pkg2, pkg3]: what's changed\r\n2. *: what's changed\r\n\r\n-->\r\n\r\n### What problem does this PR solve?\r\n<!--\r\n\r\nPlease create an issue first to describe the problem.\r\n\r\nThere MUST be one line starting with \"Issue Number:  \" and \r\nlinking the relevant issues via the \"close\" or \"ref\".\r\n\r\nFor more info, check https://pingcap.github.io/tidb-dev-guide/contribute-to-tidb/contribute-code.html#referring-to-an-issue.\r\n\r\n-->\r\n\r\nIssue Number: close #47427\r\n\r\nProblem Summary:\r\n\r\n### What is changed and how it works?\r\n\r\nIn previous implementation, partial worker will transfer full data to final worker and the final worker will copy data that belongs to it at local. However, partial worker could transfer part of full data to the final worker and it will save many memory.\r\n\r\n### Performance\r\n\r\nTiDB Version: a3bafcdffb10(nightly)\r\nTopology: 1*tidb 3*tikv\r\nDataset: tpch10\r\nSql1(high cardinality): select l_orderkey from tpch10.lineitem group by l_orderkey having sum(l_quantity) > 300;\r\nSql2(low cardinality): select l_discount from tpch10.lineitem group by l_discount;\r\n\r\n<html>\r\n<body>\r\n<!--StartFragment--><div data-page-id=\"CfhXdGrX5oAjdIxaJdMcvyWNn6b\" data-docx-has-block-data=\"true\"><div data-type=\"sheet\" class=\" old-record-id-Wo2Gd81G1oDoMox1grZcznKunjf\"><!--StartFragment--><byte-sheet-html-origin data-id=\"\" data-version=\"4\" data-is-embed=\"true\" data-grid-line-hidden=\"false\" data-copy-type=\"col\">\r\n\r\n Benchmark | Sql1 | Sql2\r\n-- | -- | --\r\nNot improved | 14.88 | 1.8\r\nImproved | 9.46 | 1.8\r\n  | 57.30% | 0%\r\n\r\n</byte-sheet-html-origin><!--EndFragment--></div></div><span data-lark-record-data=\"{&quot;isCut&quot;:false,&quot;rootId&quot;:&quot;CfhXdGrX5oAjdIxaJdMcvyWNn6b&quot;,&quot;parentId&quot;:&quot;CfhXdGrX5oAjdIxaJdMcvyWNn6b&quot;,&quot;blockIds&quot;:[22],&quot;recordIds&quot;:[&quot;Wo2Gd81G1oDoMox1grZcznKunjf&quot;],&quot;recordMap&quot;:{&quot;Wo2Gd81G1oDoMox1grZcznKunjf&quot;:{&quot;id&quot;:&quot;Wo2Gd81G1oDoMox1grZcznKunjf&quot;,&quot;snapshot&quot;:{&quot;parent_id&quot;:&quot;CfhXdGrX5oAjdIxaJdMcvyWNn6b&quot;,&quot;comments&quot;:[],&quot;locked&quot;:false,&quot;hidden&quot;:false,&quot;author&quot;:&quot;7103344350649958402&quot;,&quot;token&quot;:&quot;PRmYskrHEhJHA4tIZX9cPrumnce_f5PtdH&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;sheet&quot;}},&quot;CfhXdGrX5oAjdIxaJdMcvyWNn6b&quot;:{&quot;id&quot;:&quot;CfhXdGrX5oAjdIxaJdMcvyWNn6b&quot;,&quot;snapshot&quot;:{&quot;parent_id&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;hidden&quot;:false,&quot;text&quot;:{&quot;initialAttributedTexts&quot;:{&quot;text&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:&quot;Improved Parallel Hash Agg Benchmark&quot;},&quot;attribs&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:&quot;*0+10&quot;}},&quot;apool&quot;:{&quot;nextNum&quot;:1,&quot;numToAttrib&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:[&quot;author&quot;,&quot;7103344350649958402&quot;]}}},&quot;doc_info&quot;:{&quot;options&quot;:[&quot;editors&quot;,&quot;create_time&quot;],&quot;deleted_editors&quot;:null,&quot;editors&quot;:[&quot;7103344350649958402&quot;]},&quot;type&quot;:&quot;page&quot;,&quot;locked&quot;:false,&quot;author&quot;:&quot;7103344350649958402&quot;,&quot;children&quot;:[&quot;H1ufdpV9ioO4lUxiaLqcjOMknSb&quot;,&quot;W4LLdPcgfo7BKzxctMRcoWeKnDp&quot;,&quot;PluUdp37foKx34x6jOUcrQErnUd&quot;,&quot;PuUedh1tvoiQHoxarIYcSAx2n9j&quot;,&quot;GjCwd5cz3oU5nlx5WYbcQoPZntd&quot;,&quot;OObtdI5Hlo6aybxp8z1cYdmkntW&quot;,&quot;Wo2Gd81G1oDoMox1grZcznKunjf&quot;,&quot;MgRJdhI3VotqWYxdcoycnnLYnYg&quot;,&quot;LYljduzjLoRFilxmQzccLdcunUh&quot;,&quot;C8NjdeCBuo45o9xrbJtcYjmCnFg&quot;],&quot;align&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;comments&quot;:null}}},&quot;payloadMap&quot;:{},&quot;extra&quot;:{&quot;mention_page_title&quot;:{},&quot;external_mention_url&quot;:{}},&quot;isKeepQuoteContainer&quot;:false,&quot;selection&quot;:[{&quot;id&quot;:22,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;block&quot;,&quot;recordId&quot;:&quo